## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="9b9b0-685">O <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> classe está obsoleta no [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b9b0-685">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> class is obsolete in [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)].</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9b9b0-686">Você pode criar um Validando <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instância usando o <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> classe e o <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> método.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b9b0-686">You can create a validating <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> class and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9b9b0-687">Para obter mais informações, consulte a seção de Comentários da página de referência <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b9b0-687">For more information, see the Remarks section of the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> reference page.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9b9b0-688">O usuário precisa para testar se o tipo retornado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b9b0-688">The user needs to test for the returned type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9b9b0-689">Por exemplo,</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b9b0-689">For example,</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
object obj = vreader.SchemaType;  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaType)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaType st = (XmlSchemaType)obj;  
   // use XmlSchemaType object  
 }  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaDatatype)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaDatatype sd = (XmlSchemaDatatype)obj;  
   Type vt = sd.ValueType;  
   // use XmlSchemaDatatype object  
       }  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9b9b0-690">Se a validação de esquema XML está sendo executada, o `XmlSchemaType` ou `XmlSchemaDatatype` corresponde ao elemento atual que está sendo lido.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b9b0-690">If XML Schema validation is being performed, the `XmlSchemaType` or `XmlSchemaDatatype` corresponds to the current element being read.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9b9b0-691">Se a definição de tipo de documento (validação de DTD) está sendo executada, essa propriedade retornará `null`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b9b0-691">If document type definition (DTD validation) is being performed, this property returns `null`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9b9b0-692">`XmlSchemaDatatype` será retornado se o elemento atual ou o atributo, é um tipo simples que pode especificar restrições de validação especial nos tipos simples, como min e max.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b9b0-692">`XmlSchemaDatatype` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a simple type that can specify special validation constraints on the simple types, like min and max.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9b9b0-693">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` será retornado se o elemento atual ou o atributo, é um simpleType definidas pelo usuário.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b9b0-693">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a user defined simpleType.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9b9b0-694">`XmlSchemaComplexType` será retornado se o elemento atual for um complexType definidas pelo usuário.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b9b0-694">`XmlSchemaComplexType` is returned if the current element is a user defined complexType.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9b9b0-695">Esse tipo não pode ser retornado por atributos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b9b0-695">This type cannot be returned by attributes.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="9b9b0-696">Se <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> tiver sido definido para ValidationType.None, nenhuma informação de tipo de dados é fornecida de esquemas ou DTDs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b9b0-696">If <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> has been set to ValidationType.None, no data type information is provided from either schemas or DTDs.</span></span>  
  
> [!CAUTION]
>  <span data-ttu-id="9b9b0-697">Depois de chamar <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>, SchemaType retornará Null.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9b9b0-697">After calling <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>, SchemaType will return Null.</span></span>  
  
   
  
